  "plan": "## TCGA.ssGSEA.ROC GenePattern Module — Implementation Plan\n\n### 1. Overview\nTCGA.ssGSEA.ROC is a GenePattern module that Pipeline for ssGSEA_ROC analysis of TCGA samples\n\n### 2. Parameters\nThe module exposes 6 parameters:\n- Required: TCGA.SampleSelection1.TCGA.Collection, TCGA.SampleSelection1.Gene.Symbol, TCGA.SampleSelection1.High.Expression, TCGA.SampleSelection1.Low.Expression, ssGSEA2.gene.sets.database.files, ssGSEA2.min.gene.set.size\n- Optional: none\n\n### 3. Command Line\n```\n<java>  -Dgenepattern.properties\\=<resources> -DLSID\\=<LSID> -DPIPELINE_ARG.StopAfterTask\\=<PIPELINE_ARG.StopAfterTask> -DGenePatternURL\\=<GenePatternURL>  org.genepattern.server.webapp.RunPipelineSoap <GenePatternURL>getPipelineModel.jsp?name\\=<LSID>&userid\\=<userid> <userid> TCGA.SampleSelection1.TCGA.Collection\\=<TCGA.SampleSelection1.TCGA.Collection> TCGA.SampleSelection1.Gene.Symbol\\=<TCGA.SampleSelection1.Gene.Symbol> TCGA.SampleSelection1.High.Expression\\=<TCGA.SampleSelection1.High.Expression> TCGA.SampleSelection1.Low.Expression\\=<TCGA.SampleSelection1.Low.Expression> ssGSEA2.gene.sets.database.files\\=<ssGSEA2.gene.sets.database.files> ssGSEA2.min.gene.set.size\\=<ssGSEA2.min.gene.set.size>\n```\n\n### 4. Docker Image\nDocker image: \n\n### 5. Validation Strategy\n- Validate all required parameters are provided\n- Validate file formats match expected extensions\n- Check parameter value ranges where applicable\n\n### 6. Implementation Roadmap\nPhase 1: Wrapper script implementation\nPhase 2: Docker container setup\nPhase 3: Parameter validation and error handling\nPhase 4: Testing and documentation",
  "wrapper_script": "wrapper.sh",
